    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 \u2728 **Stunning Mint Condition \u2014 Don't Miss This One!** We are genuinely excited to bring this beautiful vehicle to market, and we'll say it straight: this car is in true mint condition inside and out! The exterior is flawless \u2014 no dings, scratches, or blemishes to speak of \u2014 and the interior looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Mechanically, everything is in top-notch shape, running smoothly and reliably. Whether you're looking for a turn-key daily driver or a showpiece addition to your collection, this is the real deal. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will speak for itself!",
