    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Absolutely Stunning & Move-In Ready \u2014 A True Mint Condition Find! This beauty is the real deal \u2014 mint condition inside and out, and it shows at every glance. The exterior gleams with no visible scratches, dents, or blemishes, and the interior is fresh, clean, and feels barely touched. Everything works exactly as it should, from the smooth-running engine to all the creature comforts inside. If you've been searching for a used car that feels as close to new as possible without the new-car price tag, this is your moment. Don't let this one slip away \u2014 mint condition finds like this don't last long on the market!",
      "price": 45000.0,
