      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a well-maintained, reliable car that has been cared for and is ready for daily driving. The exterior presents nicely overall, with the finish retaining good color and shine, though you will notice some minor surface scratches and light scuffs consistent with normal everyday use. There are no major dents, rust, or structural concerns to report. The interior is clean and functional, with the upholstery showing modest wear on high-contact areas such as the driver's seat and door panels, but no tears or significant damage. All primary controls, windows, and features operate as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and reliably, and the vehicle has been kept up with routine maintenance. The tires have good remaining tread, and the brakes are in serviceable condition. This is an honest, solid buy for someone looking for dependable transportation without paying a premium for showroom-level cosmetics.",
      "price": 36000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is presented in truly mint condition \u2014 an exceptional example that stands out even in a market full of well-maintained used cars. The exterior is flawless: the paint is deep, glossy, and free of any scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes, and every body panel sits perfectly aligned with no signs of prior collision or repair work. The interior is equally impressive, with all surfaces, upholstery, and trim looking and smelling as fresh as the day it left the showroom \u2014 no fading, cracking, staining, or wear to report anywhere. Mechanically, this car is in outstanding shape: the engine runs with smooth, confident power, all systems function exactly as intended, and the service history is clean and complete with no deferred maintenance. Tires, brakes, and all wear items are in excellent condition with substantial life remaining. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle with zero compromises \u2014 ideal for a discerning buyer who wants the reliability and feel of a new car at a used-car price.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $18,500, a price that honestly reflects its fair condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. The exterior shows visible wear consistent with regular use: there are several scratches and minor dings on the body panels, and the paint has faded noticeably in certain areas, particularly on the hood and roof. The interior is functional but shows clear signs of age \u2014 the upholstery has some staining and wear on the driver's seat, and a few trim pieces are slightly loose or scuffed. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it is not without issues: expect that some maintenance or repairs may be needed in the near term, and we encourage any serious buyer to have an independent mechanic inspect the vehicle before purchase. The tires have moderate tread remaining, and all major systems (engine, transmission, brakes) are operational, though not in peak form. This is a practical, budget-conscious option for a buyer who understands they are getting a used vehicle in fair \u2014 not excellent \u2014 shape.",
